## ‚ö° Bonus Tools for Modern Linux Power Users
| Tool | Description |
|------|--------------|
| `fzf` | Fuzzy finder for files and command history |
| `ripgrep (rg)` | Fast recursive text search |
| `bat` | Syntax-highlighted `cat` alternative |
| `exa` | Modern replacement for `ls` |
| `btop` | Beautiful resource monitor |
| `fd` | Fast `find` replacement |
| `ncdu` | TUI disk usage analyzer |
| `glances` | Comprehensive system monitor |
| `tokei` | Count lines of code by language |

---

> üí° **Tip:** Combine commands creatively ‚Äî e.g.  
> `ps aux | grep nginx | awk '{print $2}' | xargs kill -9`  
> or  
> `find . -type f -print0 | xargs -0 du -ch | sort -rh | head -20`

